title: Johnny Smith quintets MOONLIGHT IN VERMONT (1952) Getz,Zoot
description:
As an indicator of Johnny Smith's importance to the guitar, there are (3)

special models of guitar named for and designed by him from 3 different

makers: Gibson, Guild, and Heritage (although Gibson and Heritage are

closely related companies)


Johnny Smith was comfortable playing in the studio or reading music with an 

orchestra.  Greatly admired by other musicians, he was a paragon of musicianship.


Johnny Smith (1922-2013)   (new to the database)
